es/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec54e24d26bda1bd649bce54ce1e528b2eb2f41","tid":2511080,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"與其感情用事不如讀杜甫的《望岳》<br />\n<br />\n岱宗夫如何？齊魯青未了。<br />\n造化鍾神秀，陰陽割昏曉。<br />\n盪胸生曾雲，決眥入歸鳥。<br />\n會當凌絕頂，一覽眾山小。"},{"pid":"e87751f86325e20df0923f7ce67d333db631e0cf","tid":2511080,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"王方一聽，馬上覺得此名最佳，同時之間，王弗在閨房亦想了一名。丫環把王弗題字的紙讓王方看，竟然和東坡一樣，是「喚魚池」！王方說：「此乃天緣之合，韻成雙璧。」<br />\n<br />\n十足十電影劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n王弗逝世，東坡執筆寫下墓誌銘，憶起王弗怎樣陪自己讀書，怎樣為了自己的粗心，仔細提點，所有言行都是因愛而生，溫柔體貼。<br />\n<br />\n東坡父親，曾特意提醒東坡說：王弗在你還沒有什麼成就時，就開始就跟著你，同甘共苦，未來一定要將她，與汝母合葬。<br />\n<br />\n識於微時,志趣相投又溫柔體貼,真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd81752d1f4452bf2ebcbb56ba4f1bc67ef29bc5","tid":2511080,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f9d4da8818f6739a35cab0963175aa31547639","tid":2511080,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1876cc72e83a3fa44edacbf3041aa12b11216ab4","tid":2511080,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31c1d632b6624e5e96c4ac4322060e1aee832a39","tid":2511080,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗即寫都無咁感人<br />\n十年之後，仲念念不忘夢見妻子<br />\n呢種深情真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"「夢斷香消四十年，沈園柳老不吹綿」都係深情人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打識貨，陸遊都係好出色嘅詞家"},{"pid":"b055f9ae17876805ea04dc3e201493e7c2647d58","tid":2511080,"uid":128869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"本身寫緊野都俾探長吸引咗嚟追POST<br />\n<br />\n各位可以睇睇蔣勳當係一個補充<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8O3jMPUKFs&amp;t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC8O3jMPUKFs%26t%3D2s&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqREXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e4b4b728\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8O3jMPUKFs&amp;t=2s</a><br />\n17：00開始"},{"pid":"3f276bac354f31eceaca0d2fe48a00353a0f4c5b","tid":2511080,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"戈登探長你堅係有毅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bddebb449d45f2a4a7709807dc84f0befc6cec4","tid":2511080,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc4cd824c8ee31daacc219f5e1f70edab2dc0da4","tid":2511080,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9b880176925d7b23ca4fe479cad039043bd6d6","tid":2511080,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79bf27d1c1c2744720b3b61fce8c773e139877dd","tid":2511080,"uid":240713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"中學睇到喊嘅一首詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絲打係咪自己睇到？<br />\n中學課本我記憶中好似無呢篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"文學有喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" cl